comments.body: Needs some compat bounds to avoid resolver bug.

I tried to create a release but ran into this error:
```
POST https://api.github.com/repos/FluxML/Trebuchet.jl/releases: 422 Validation Failed [{Resource:Release Field:tag_name Code:already_exists Message:}]
```
To retry, comment on this PR with the phrase `TagBot tag`.
cc: @christopher-dG
